      "_note": "Vocabulary-flexible from the model side: meaning-of-life-class queries have no canonical phrasing in the system prompt, so the model improvises in-voice (PR #26's first-run surfaced 'Not my department'). Using refusal_detected:true here would force REFUSAL_PHRASES to grow every time the model picks a new in-voice phrasing — a rubber-stamp loop that drains the literal-match assertion's signal. The voice-family contains_any tail is the honest assertion. Phase 5 will survey which other queries are phrase-bound vs vocabulary-flexible.",
      "assertions": [
